	<p><font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="2" color="#FFFFFF">Hey I decided I would post again. My original point had nothing to do with the EULA. If you are really feel adimant about the EULA that is fine. There is nothing I can say about that. My point was aside from that people tend to frown on people buying pp ( because it is a waste of money )even though they do the same thing just in other ways.<br />
