-dual boxers <br />
-etc..<br />
People waste money all the time. I feel if it is their money they can do with it what they wish Even if it means buying a 5 dollar hotdog at a football game. Whatever makes you happy. More to ya.<br />
<br />
P.S. In my original post I said that pp duping is wrong. However if someone legitimately earns their pp and sells it to another person that does not hurt the EQ economy. The money simply changes hands</font></p>
	
