	<tr><td colspan="2" bgcolor="#666699" vAlign="TOP">
	<p><font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="2" color="#FFFFFF">I am not a "I'm OK, your OK" kind of guy.  I think it is pathetic that anyone would waste more money than their monthly fee to play this game.  There are plenty of ways to make in game money with out breaking your agreement.  Paying for ingame money not only screws up the economy ingame but limits the camps the rest of us can get.  I am sure you all are aware of the idiots these people employ to camp the big ticket items to sell in the bazaar.  A lot of these items are perma camped because of these plat generators.  They camp the items, so you cant.  Then they post the items for sale in the bazaar at inflated prices, which you can't afford.  So you are tempted to buy plat from them so you can give it back to their mule in the bazaar for the item that you could not camp because they were their first and will always be there. <br />
<br />
"Norvik breaths"<br />
<br />
You shoot yourself in the foot when you join into this, and not just yourself but everyone on your server.</font></p>
	
	<p><p><img src="/forums/images/sig_separator.gif" width="282" height="11" Alt="Hey! Watch where you point that thing!"><br>
